parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag light can indicate a malfunction in the airbag system, which can lead to failure to deploy in the event of a crash, potentially resulting in injuries or fatalities.

sometimes accompanied by a chime or beep.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of a crash can result in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag does not deploy in a crash

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The Takata airbag recall can lead to the failure of the airbag to deploy or deploy improperly, resulting in injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The vehicle is subject to the Takata airbag recall
